---
title: Cajun Jumbo Shrimp and Fennel Stew with Wild Rice Medley and Fresh Salad
description: Nothing hits the spot like a good shrimp stew! Succulent jumbo shrimp are the key players in this stew featuring Cajun Spice Blend, crushed tomatoes, corn, fennel and roasted red pepper pesto. A refreshing salad tossed with clementines and goat cheese is the perfect side for this hearty meal.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/ragout-de-crevettes-geantes-et-de-fenouil-5706668d.jpg
